---
title: Climber State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> EXTENDING : Command sets EXTENDING
    EXTENDING --> IDLE : Command sets IDLE

    IDLE --> RETRACTING : Command sets RETRACTING
    RETRACTING --> IDLE : Command sets IDLE

    EXTENDING --> RETRACTING : Command sets RETRACTING
    RETRACTING --> EXTENDING : Command sets EXTENDING

    IDLE --> LOCKED : Command sets LOCKED
    EXTENDING --> LOCKED : Command sets LOCKED
    RETRACTING --> LOCKED : Command sets LOCKED
    LOCKED --> IDLE : Command sets IDLE

    note right of IDLE
        Motor stopped
        Climber at rest
    end note

    note right of EXTENDING
        Motor extending climber arm
    end note

    note right of RETRACTING
        Motor retracting climber arm
    end note

    note right of LOCKED
        Climber locked in position
        Holds robot weight
    end note
